{
  "texts": [
    "As part of the survey, participants were asked to provide information about their age, gender, and previous military assignments.",
    "Data were collected via a digital questionnaire in PDF format.",
    "The email address used to send the questionnaire was deleted after the survey was completed.",
    "Raw data from the experts included in the statistical analysis were anonymized, as well.",
    "Participants in the study were randomly assigned to either the experimental or control group."
  ]
}